		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;输入“Chinese”后,选择第一个，然后点击下载&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE04.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1526&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE04_hu_ab900d54219c0a69.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE04_hu_8b7775064d42b14.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;vscode设置04&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;安装完毕后，重启vscode之后就显示中文了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;除此之外，我们还要下载C/C++插件&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDC%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1527&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDC%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6_hu_74f12463842fd4df.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDC%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6_hu_d835519a66ff7295.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;vscode下载C语言插件&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们再下载code runner插件，这个插件能够让你使用CTRL+ALT+N来运行代码&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDCodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1525&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDCodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6_hu_4e9bdde48ea5ec21.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/vscode%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDCodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6_hu_410666f0b5dc9e0d.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;vscode下载Code Runner插件&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在此之前让我帮你设置好Code Runner&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;让我们回到首页&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE01.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1526&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE01_hu_a37f3bf77b4789b.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE01_hu_9137857b3e467a09.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Code Runner插件设置01&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后通过按你的键盘上CTRL + ，这两个键来进入设置界面&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE02.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1525&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE02_hu_d6c70aa64ddeeed4.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE02_hu_6fd3be52a37bcd16.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Code Runner插件设置02&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在搜索栏，搜索Code Runner,然后勾选 Run In Terminal ，Save All Files Before Run ，Save File Before Run&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE03.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1527&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE03_hu_ef0826e0c8ced209.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE03_hu_ca81a066899745f9.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Code Runner插件设置03&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后再点击“在setting.json中编辑”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE04.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1526&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE04_hu_5801ae332cfa0da9.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE04_hu_7f0e23bda4e76b0a.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Code Runner插件设置04&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;设置成这个样子&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;c&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;chcp 65001 &amp;gt; $null; cd $dir; gcc -Wall -Wextra -O2 \&amp;#34;$fileName\&amp;#34; -o \&amp;#34;./bin/$fileNameWithoutExt.exe\&amp;#34;; ./bin/\&amp;#34;$fileNameWithoutExt.exe\&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;cpp&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;chcp 65001 &amp;gt; $null; if (!(Test-Path bin)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Name bin | Out-Null }; cd $dir; g++ -Wall -Wextra -O2 -static \&amp;#34;$fileName\&amp;#34; -o \&amp;#34;bin/$fileNameWithoutExt.exe\&amp;#34;; if ($LASTEXITCODE -eq 0) { Write-Host &amp;#39;Running...&amp;#39; -ForegroundColor Green; &amp;amp; \&amp;#34;bin/$fileNameWithoutExt.exe\&amp;#34; } else { Write-Host &amp;#39;Compilation failed!&amp;#39; -ForegroundColor Red }&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE05.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1524&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE05_hu_e35ecb5da2e3727e.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/CodeRunner%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE05_hu_2213156a733e0b95.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Code Runner插件设置05&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;为什么要这么设置呢？这行命令用于在 PowerShell 中一键编译并运行 C 程序：先通过 &lt;code&gt;chcp 65001&lt;/code&gt; 切换控制台为 UTF-8 编码以避免中文乱码，再切换到源文件目录确保路径正确；接着用 &lt;code&gt;gcc -Wall -Wextra -O2&lt;/code&gt; 启用严格警告和优化，将源文件编译为 &lt;code&gt;./bin/&lt;/code&gt; 目录下的同名 &lt;code&gt;.exe&lt;/code&gt; 可执行文件，保持项目整洁；最后自动运行该程序，实现高效、可靠、用户友好的开发体验。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;不过要注意！！！！！！的一点是要记得在你的文件夹中新建一个名字为“bin”的文件夹，用来存放你的因为源文件编译而产生的同名的.exe文件&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8CC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2559&#34;
	height=&#34;1522&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8CC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6_hu_90576f3dc3f0d591.png 480w, https://Lin100101.github.io/p/vs-code-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-c/c-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8CC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6_hu_b2fe01017121e9ae.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;运行C文件&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;168&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;403px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;至此，我们能够在VSCode中编写并且能够运行C语言代码了，&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
